{"tid":1487233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【更新】【登報突發】大家係時侯瘋狂叫外國人睇報紙同請廣傳！","createTime":"2019-08-19T07:38:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T14:08:07.000Z","uid":50983,"like":136,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"b4d6876941ef7c4228cfab469c791e2bf2f34a2c","tid":1487233,"uid":50983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:38:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【道歉聲明】出版日期資料錯誤，原公佈表示19號會出版的三份英國報章將更正為20號出版，特此通知。令英國朋友白走一趟，深感歉意。</span><br />\n<br />\n各位連登巴絲、hueng gong yen<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">今日（8月19）</span>，我地嘅廣告會喺全世界<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">10個國家</span></span></strong>，總共<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">11份報章</span></span></strong>面世<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊呼籲國際關注香港人面對嘅警暴問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過往七十幾日，香港發生無數人道災難，<span style=\"color: orange;\">警方嘅種種暴行令人髮指</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nG20 x 攬炒團隊是次合作，就係希望可以揭露警方所干犯各種濫權、濫捕、違反戰爭法或國際人道法嘅罪行，呼籲國際社會關注香港飽受文明社會中嘅不文明對待<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n並同時呼籲外國人繼續支持香港人嘅抗爭運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8月19日面世報章包括：<br />\n🇺🇸 美國《紐約時報》The New York Times<br />\n🇨🇦 加拿大《環球郵報》The Globe and Mail<br />\n🇯🇵 日本《日本經濟新聞》Nihon Keizai Shinbun<br />\n🇰🇷 韓國《京鄉新聞》Kyunghyang Shinmun<br />\n🇪🇸 西班牙《世界報》El mundo<br />\n🇩🇪 德國《法蘭克福滙報》Frankfurter Allgemeine (FAZ)<br />\n🇹🇼 台灣《自由時報》The Liberty Times<br />\n🇫🇷 法國《世界報》Le Monde <br />\n🇸🇪 瑞典《每日新聞報》Dagens Nyheter<br />\n🇸🇪 瑞典《每日工業報》Dagens Industri<br />\n🇩🇰 丹麥《貝林時報》Berlingske<br />\n<br />\n我地誠邀身處外地嘅巴絲廣泛傳播公開信，當實體報章到手後，加上自己嘅訊息並加上 #FreedomHK 及 #StandWithHK，再share俾各社交平台，等更多人明白香港嘅困境，共挽狂瀾於既倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次合作嘅兩個團隊之間分工明確，全盤計劃唔會只得登報，所以G20團隊淨係負責登報相關嘅統籌，其他事宜（包括一切會計、法律及所有後續計劃）均由攬炒團隊負責，大家敬請期待攬炒團隊嘅行動！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下方便大家集郵同埋share俾人做文宣圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kyX04Nf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkyX04Nf.jpg&h=d8eb4275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2QSwr0B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2QSwr0B.jpg&h=e0d3455e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zrUSbsg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzrUSbsg.jpg&h=34d8000f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5fWdFkC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5fWdFkC.jpg&h=96b3602b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DE7MfTX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDE7MfTX.jpg&h=a5e0e9d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NGxkkkC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNGxkkkC.jpg&h=1ef242dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oWvNKNi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoWvNKNi.jpg&h=0be93781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K2H04Ni.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK2H04Ni.jpg&h=9af3ebf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Nah60D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Nah60D.jpg&h=63256e17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KDpF4Nj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKDpF4Nj.jpg&h=0adf9705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEOWC7j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEOWC7j.jpg&h=6824717f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSorry for 金鋼棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">-----<br />\n有關眾籌活動嘅最新消息，可參閱以下頻道。<br />\nFacebook 專頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/freedomhkgofficial/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffreedomhkgofficial%2F&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF469mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=54ceebd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/freedomhkgofficial/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standwithhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandwithhk%2F&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF469mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=d2bcd8bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standwithhk/</a><br />\nTelegram Channel： <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/FreedomHKG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FFreedomHKG&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF469mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=48175029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/FreedomHKG</a><br />\nTwitter： <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/FreedomHKG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFreedomHKG&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF469mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=6d4f12b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/FreedomHKG</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF469mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=42f55c00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK</a><br />\nInstagram： <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/FreedomHKG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2FFreedomHKG&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF469mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=87761bc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/FreedomHKG</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/standwithhk_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fstandwithhk_%2F&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF469mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=61c06a29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/standwithhk_/</a><br />\n#antiELAB #FreedomHK #StandwithHK</span><br />\n<br />\n＊有關G20團隊的一切消息以Facebook Page Freedom HONG KONG 作準。＊"},{"pid":"950a2908047ffbfc7d93ea3bfb97331e73412b74","tid":1487233,"uid":164568,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:38:53.000Z","msg":"我愛家樂牌"},{"pid":"e4000a28bd0f7aef3fde0d7b0077075feb964873","tid":1487233,"uid":164568,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:39:09.000Z","msg":"家樂牌通心粉係我老公"},{"pid":"9da46fff4d721fb122177b31997b4602c52f65bb","tid":1487233,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:39:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e49d57d744200a81a5178cddb1e4b2afe8c4ee03","tid":1487233,"uid":164568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:39:21.000Z","msg":"家樂牌我鍾意你"},{"pid":"f341b2958609e39b9fee931c6504763a65ffc33b","tid":1487233,"uid":173806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:39:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3dfd86d5f373c5ee95c6e73ccd3026699ca48b24","tid":1487233,"uid":260557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:39:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im